cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS 

The paper deals with optimization of machine learning models, specifically stochastic gradient descent, which is a popular algorithm in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of online convex optimization algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the application of the proposed method in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with optimization of non-convex functions, which falls under the category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
